<h3>Review</h3>

<p>Looking back, this week wasn’t perfect, but it was meaningful. Wins like launching ideas into action (upcoach, SumBox and WeekVista), engaging deeply with my team and people I'm working with, and rediscovering my long-term vision balanced out the challenges. My key takeaway? Staying true to my core values makes even the hardest days worthwhile.</p>

<p>Balance is not about perfection but about making the most of what matters—whether it’s shipping a feature, brainstorming a new idea, or cherishing time with family. This week was a testament to that.</p>

